{"tid":1403854,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"〔超合作運動〕香港人必勝法","createTime":"2019-08-03T23:55:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T13:23:37.000Z","uid":294873,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"1d438fdb41cc478f4a2846cb443a0e8793143308","tid":1403854,"uid":294873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T23:55:41.000Z","msg":"我哋係一班駕駛人士，見到近嚟香港大變，變得有啲陌生。我哋揸車嘅人要份外留神。所以我哋呢班司機舉行《限速保香港平安》計劃，希望所有香港人平平安安。由8月5日凌晨0:00開始：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>1. 按限速指示駕駛車輛<br />\n2. 保持2 - 3秒行車距離<br />\n3. 出入迴旋處格外留神</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n因著香港情況有機會愈變愈陌生，所以我們不排除在未來日子將駕駛時速降低，及增加行車距離，以保障香港人安全。<br />\n<br />\n為咗令大家好似係鄉下揸車咁提醒道路使用者小心啲，我哋同時印製數百個和風貼紙，以供更多駕駛者參與《限速保香港平安》計劃。大家可以在發夢時向我們索取，或自行印製貼在車尾顯眼位置上。好人一生平安。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fy39psv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFy39psv.jpg&h=b46c0d01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GTpXykQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGTpXykQ.jpg&h=13284be8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bS7Y2eb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbS7Y2eb.jpg&h=0733a9e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W1cx6FS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW1cx6FS.jpg&h=c57690b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VhypXNy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVhypXNy.jpg&h=96ca40c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KVfsa7z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKVfsa7z.jpg&h=1b1a227f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1XTtE0V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1XTtE0V.jpg&h=84834373&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n#我係香港人 <br />\n#我會參與8月5日三罷 <br />\n#罷工罷市罷課"},{"pid":"043f83b4606c5e03c3407ea2e3ed7f4be737eccf","tid":1403854,"uid":50286,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T23:56:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OBzMrF0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOBzMrF0.png&h=eb879a09&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3f6116041810bb8a30b939af3bc89f1813a803df","tid":1403854,"uid":188870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T00:05:59.000Z","msg":"必推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1901acdb8d9d934b26c6aed0ca9f170a9de538a","tid":1403854,"uid":294873,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T00:06:12.000Z","msg":"有興趣參與下一步行動，可add TG group: 限速保香港平安"},{"pid":"5a3a5e26b26db989a253974ce65b65b0e517f434","tid":1403854,"uid":295784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T00:08:45.000Z","msg":"推！平安駕駛！"},{"pid":"9f58f3f579097fdd1f37f0ac4c6db3142be3955c","tid":1403854,"uid":255336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T02:02:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac4d58ed20db2b382ee9bdb74f9e01bbfe119f1f","tid":1403854,"uid":287580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T02:06:33.000Z","msg":"唔錯👍🏼👍🏼👍🏼👍🏼"},{"pid":"e0a5bdc8c7f4e3a4c5ecedd8952946b743b9df1b","tid":1403854,"uid":22312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T02:17:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f7a644c13b50af1788a25f46add7df8f8c47cb08","tid":1403854,"uid":255336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T03:03:49.000Z","msg":"越多人貼越安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"380f884f8df225d2685897b7b01dad13a6a663a6","tid":1403854,"uid":255336,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T03:04:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XMc99XM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXMc99XM.p